    "description": "Type any verse in the Bible and record your best WPM for each verse-set (1 - 2 verses per set).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Type the entire Bible in any order you like.</li></ul>Word is a non-linear typing game in which you can type any book, chapter or verse in the Bible.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Record your highest WPM for each verse-set.</li></ul><strong>Each menu and button show your progress and best WPM.<br>Replay levels to improve your stats!</strong><br>Think of Word as a long term game with tons of replay value; over time, type the entire Bible or just one book or just the famous verses and then go back to improve your score. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Record your most efficient performance for each verse-set.</li></ul>Navigating the menus, if you have played the level previously, your best performance will be displayed; efficiency score increases with both higher-WPM and fewer-mistakes.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Featuring instrumental hip hop by Fidget !! </li></ul>Includes an ample sampling of super talented audio genius, Fidget! Choose his playlist on the options menu; the default gameplay audio is a satisfying Chopin piano playlist.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Word makes use of the World English Bible (WEBP)</li></ul>The World English Bible is a Public Domain Modern English translation of the Holy Bible.",
